<lb n="0541c08" ed="X"/><lb n="0898b08" ed="R012"/><cb:juan n="8" fun="close"><cb:jhead>大方廣佛華嚴經綱要卷第八</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</cb:div></cb:div></body></text></TEI>